4.2 Scraping process
def parse(response):
list_links = response.css(LIST_OF_LINKS)
for document in response.css(LIST_OF_DOCUMENTS):
links = list_links[counter]
meta_data = {
'pdf_url': PDF_URL,
'abstract_url': ABSTRACT_URL,
'doc_id': doc_id,
'title': response.css(TITLE),
'authors': response.css(AUTHORS),
'subject': response.css(SUBJECT),
'other_subjects': response.css(OTHER_SUBJECTS)
}
yield scrapy.Request(url = ABSTRACT_URL,
callback=parse_abstract,
meta=meta_data)
doc_id += 1
counter += 1
Scrapy
def parse_abstract(response):
abstract = response.xpath(ABSTRACT)
submit_date = response.css(SUBMIT_DATE)
response.meta.update({'abstract': abstract)
response.meta.update({'submit_date': submit_date)
yield scrapy.Request(url=PDF_URL, callback=parse_pdf,
meta=response.meta)
